com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.security

Class SecurityConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.veraxsystems.vxipmi.coding.security.SecurityConstants

  • public final class SecurityConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    Set of constants. Byte constants are encoded as pseudo unsigned bytes. SecurityConstants doesn't use TypeConverter because fields need to be runtime constants.
    See Also:
    TypeConverter.byteToInt(byte), TypeConverter.intToByte(int)
